Class EuropeanChess

  • java.lang.Object
    • EuropeanChess
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ChessGame
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EuropeanChessTest

    public class EuropeanChess
extends java.lang.Object
implements ChessGame
    A class that implements the rules of european chess through determining which side is legal to play, and moving pieces from when their move is legal. It also implements the main method that creates the chessboard with all the playing pawns
